('2017-2t-fdc1','* 问题：\r\n - PHP V7.1下，出现类似信息：\r\n  Illegal string offset count(*)\r\n - 版本：所有版本，在php v7.1下出现\r\n\r\n* 文件：\r\n - /imcat/code/core/glib/glbDBObj.php\r\n - 方法：function count()\r\n\r\n* 代码\r\n```\r\n$data=\"\";\r\n$this->connect();            \r\n$data[`count(*)`] = $this->db->val($this->sql);\r\n$this->runTimer(`count`);\r\nreturn $data[`count(*)`];\r\n -=> 改为\r\n$this->connect();            \r\n$re = $this->db->val($this->sql);\r\n$this->runTimer(\'count\');\r\nreturn $re;\r\n```\r\n\r\n* 原因：\r\n - PHP V7.1下，数据类型要求严格了\r\n - 本处问题，$data初始化字符串，后来又设置为数组，导致出错。\r\n','','','','','','','md'),
